topic.title: pf_2_mss_cscbreg_hsio_pair_x2y0_RB_LS_R0_I7_23 Parameter Variable Definitions
topic.shortdesc: This library includes label variables to define some Module Parameters. Each label variable is defined in a separate paragraph by means of the <msgph> element. The <msgph> attribute 'varid' should hold a unique name for the variable.
